text: The 2019 Ladies Open Hechingen was a professional tennis tournament played on outdoor clay courts. It was the twenty-first edition of the tournament which was part of the 2019 ITF Women's World Tennis Tour. It took place in Hechingen, Germany between 5 and 11 August 2019. ==Singles main draw entrants== ===Seeds=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! width="70"| Country ! width="175"| Player ! Rank1 !
